		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I dont know anything about 6502 Nes programming.
<br />
<br /><span style="color: black"><strong>1. </strong></span>Where do I start? What compiler and tutorials are recommended?
<br /><span style="color: black"><strong>2. </strong></span>Why learn it? Its an outdated thing right? ( Other then NES is awsome =D )
<br />
<br />Thanks,
